trans-unit.source: Represents an automatically generated field in a data-bound control.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en automatisk generert feltet i en databundet-kontroll.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan arves.

trans-unit.source: The AutoGeneratedField class is used to represent an automatically generated field in a data-bound control, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>.
trans-unit.target: Klassen AutoGeneratedField brukes til å representere en automatisk generert felt i en databundet kontroll, for eksempel <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: Automatically generated fields are created by a data-bound control when the appropriate property is set to `true` (for example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.AutoGenerateColumns%2A> property for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.AutoGenerateRows%2A> property for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> control, and so on).
trans-unit.target: Automatisk genererte felt er opprettet av en databundet kontroll når den nødvendige egenskapen er satt til `true` (for eksempel den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.AutoGenerateColumns%2A>egenskapen for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontroll, den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.AutoGenerateRows%2A>egenskapen for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>kontrollen og så videre).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.AutoGenerateRows%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.AutoGenerateColumns%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Automatically generated fields are not added to the field collection of a data-bound control (for example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.Columns%2A> collection for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> control, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.Fields%2A> collection for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> control, and so on).
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Automatisk genererte felt er ikke lagt til i samlingen feltet i en databundet kontroll (for eksempel den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.Columns%2A>samling for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>kontroll, den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.Fields%2A>samling for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>kontrollen og så videre).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView.Fields%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.Columns%2A>

trans-unit.source: The AutoGeneratedField class is intended for use internally by data-bound controls.
trans-unit.target: Klassen AutoGeneratedField er ment for Bruk internt av databundet kontroller.

trans-unit.source: Unlike other data fields (such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BoundField>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxField>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplateField>, and so on), the AutoGeneratedField class cannot be placed declaratively on a page as part of a field collection.
trans-unit.target: I motsetning til andre datafelt (eksempel <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BoundField>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxField>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplateField>og så videre), AutoGeneratedField klassen kan ikke plasseres deklarativt på en side som en del av en felt-samling.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplateField> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CheckBoxField> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BoundField>

trans-unit.source: Although you can programmatically add an AutoGeneratedField object to a field collection, this design pattern should be avoided.
trans-unit.target: Selv om du kan legge til et objekt som AutoGeneratedField programmatisk i en samling med felt, må denne utformingen mønsteret unngås.

trans-unit.source: Because automatically generated fields represent the automatic rendering of a field, data-bound controls do not typically allow users to modify the properties of the AutoGeneratedField objects.
trans-unit.target: Fordi automatisk genererte felt representerer automatisk gjengivelse av et felt, Tillat databundet kontroller ikke vanligvis brukere å endre egenskaper for AutoGeneratedField-objekter.

trans-unit.source: If the automatic rendering is not suitable for your needs, define your own data fields for the field collection of the control.
trans-unit.target: Hvis automatisk gjengivelsen er til dine behov, kan du definere datafeltene for samlingen felt i kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"></xref> class with the specified data field.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"> </xref> klassen med det angitte feltet.

trans-unit.source: This constructor is generally used by data-bound controls (such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>) when creating automatically generated fields.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren brukes vanligvis av databundet kontroller (eksempel <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>) når du oppretter automatisk generert felt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: The name of the data field to bind to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på datafeltet skal bindes til det <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether empty string ("") values are converted to <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> when the field values are retrieved from the data source.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om tom streng ("") konverteres til <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> når feltverdiene hentes fra datakilden.

trans-unit.source: Sometimes a field's value is an empty string ("") in the data source.
trans-unit.target: Noen ganger verdien for et felt er en tom streng ("") i datakilden.

trans-unit.source: The ConvertEmptyStringToNull property is used to indicate whether empty string values are converted to `null` before being displayed in an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ConvertEmptyStringToNull brukes til å angi om tomme strengverdier konverteres til `null` før den vises i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This version of the property has been implemented to always return `true`.

trans-unit.source: The DataFormatString property is used to apply a special format to the values displayed in an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField> object.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen DataFormatString brukes til å bruke et bestemt format på verdiene som vises i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This version of the property has been implemented to always return an empty string to indicate that no special formatting is applied to the field values.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Denne versjonen av egenskapen har blitt implementert for å returnere en tom streng til å angi at ingen spesielle formateringen til feltverdiene alltid.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the data type of the values displayed in an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir datatypen for verdiene som vises i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Use the DataType property to specify the data type of the values displayed in an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField> object.
trans-unit.target: Bruk DataType-egenskapen til å angi datatypen for verdiene som vises i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>

trans-unit.source: The data type determines what type of control is rendered in an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField> object to display the value.
trans-unit.target: Datatypen bestemmer hvilken type kontroll gjengis i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>objekt for å vise verdien.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>

trans-unit.source: For example, a check box control is displayed when the type is <xref:System.Boolean>.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel skal en avmerkingsbokskontrollen vises når typen er <xref:System.Boolean>.</xref:System.Boolean>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Type> that represents the data type of the value displayed in an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Type>som representerer datatypen for verdien som vises i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"> </xref> objektet.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref:System.String>.
trans-unit.target: Standard er <xref:System.String>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Fills the specified <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary"></xref> object with the values from the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Fyller den angitte <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary"> </xref> objektet med verdiene fra den angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The ExtractValuesFromCell method is a helper method used to retrieve the values of the fields from the specified <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell> object in an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden ExtractValuesFromCell er helper metode som brukes til å hente verdier for feltene fra den angitte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell>objekt i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This method is primarily used by control developers.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Denne metoden brukes hovedsakelig av kontrollutviklere.

trans-unit.source: This method does not have a return value.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden har ikke en returverdi.

trans-unit.source: Instead, the field values are returned by reference through the <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary> object passed in for the `dictionary` parameter.
trans-unit.target: I stedet feltverdiene returneres av referansen via den <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary>objekt sendt for den `dictionary` parameteren.</xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary>

trans-unit.source: After the method has been called, iterate through the <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary> object to access the field values.
trans-unit.target: Etter at den har blitt kalt, gå gjennom den <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary>objekt for å få tilgang til feltverdiene.</xref:System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > To include the read-only field values in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell> object, pass in `true` for the `includeReadOnly` parameter.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Inkludere skrivebeskyttet feltverdiene i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell>objekt, sendes i `true` for den `includeReadOnly` parameteren.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary"></xref> used to store the values of the specified cell.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary"> </xref> brukes til å lagre verdiene i den angitte cellen.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the controls contained in an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"></xref> object support callbacks.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer om kontrollene finnes i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField"> </xref> objekt støtte tilbakeringinger.

trans-unit.source: The ValidateSupportsCallback method is the helper method used to determine whether the controls contained in an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField> object support callbacks.
trans-unit.target: Metoden ValidateSupportsCallback er helper metoden som brukes til å bestemme om kontrollene finnes i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>objekt støtte tilbakeringinger.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AutoGeneratedField>

trans-unit.source: This method has been implemented as an empty method (a method that does not contain any code) to indicate that callbacks are supported.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden er implementert som en tom metode (en metode som ikke inneholder kode) til å angi at tilbakeringinger støttes.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This method is primarily used by control developers.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Denne metoden brukes hovedsakelig av kontrollutviklere.

trans-unit.source: Classes that derive from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> class can override this method to indicate whether the controls contained by the field support callbacks.
trans-unit.target: Klasser som er avledet fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>klassen kan overstyre denne metoden for å angi om kontrollene som inneholder feltet støtte tilbakeringinger.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: To indicate that callbacks are supported, implement this method as an empty method that does not throw an exception; otherwise, throw an exception with a useful message describing why callbacks are not supported.
trans-unit.target: Implementer denne metoden for å angi at tilbakeringinger støttes, som en tom metode som ikke iverksette et unntak; Ellers Iverksett et unntak med en nyttig melding som beskriver hvorfor tilbakeringinger støttes ikke.
